0:10:27.07,000 --> 0:10:3,000
So this was an xkcd cartoon from a couple of years ago,

271
0:10:30.488,000 --> 0:10:31,000
and the cartoonist suggests

272
0:10:32.162,000 --> 0:10:34,000
that we should all use pass phrases,

