0:12:50.033,000 --> 0:12:53,000
So it's not really a clear win for pass phrases.

334
0:12:53.26,000 --> 0:12:56,000
Sorry, all of you xkcd fans.

335
0:12:56.605,000 --> 0:12:57,000
On the other hand, we did find

